            <h2 class="red">Living with haemophilia: in the classroom. A teacher’s guide</h2>
            <p>A brief guide that can be shared with a patient’s teacher to support the management of haemophilia at school.</p>
            <p><a href="./docs/living-with-haemophilia-in-the-classroom-teachers-guide-2020.pdf" class="action" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View PDF</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tile flex half">
          <figure>
            <img src="./images/living-with-haemophilia-parents-guide.jpg" alt="Parents guide to supporting children with Haemophilia" title="Download PDF" width="150px" height="200px" />
