          <div>
            <h2 class="red">Living with haemophilia: at home. A parent’s guide to factor infusion</h2>
            <p>A brief guide to factor infusion for parents or carers of children with haemophilia.</p>
            <p><a href="./docs/living-with-haemophilia-at-home-parents-guide-2020.pdf" class="action" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View PDF</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

