            <h2 class="red">Living with haemophilia: A guide to mild and moderate haemophilia</h2>
            <p>A brief guide for patients, carers or parents of children with mild or moderate haemophilia.</p>
            <p><a href="./docs/adt01750-livin-with-haemophilia-guide-to-mild-to-moderate-haemophilia.pdf" class="action" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View PDF</a></p>
